fileContent:
bucket test_bucket:
    location: US
    storage: Standard
    access: public
    destroy: true
    tags:
        - bucket
        - new
        - logs
    lifecycle:
        - rule rule_1:
            condition:
                - age : 1
                - storage: Standard
            action: Delete
        - rule rule_2:
            condition:
                storage: Standard
            action: Delete

bucket test_bucket#i:
    location: US if #i % 2 == 0 else EU
    storage: Standard
    access: private
    tags:
        - multi_bucket
